The average remaining service period of active covered employees is eight years for Duke Energy and Duke Energy Carolinas, seven years for
Progress Energy, Duke Energy Florida, and Duke Energy Ohio, and six years for Duke Energy Progress, Duke Energy Indiana, and Piedmont.
